# My Deals — Unified Business Work Queue

## Purpose

My Deals is the operational home for RMs and business users.

- **My Deals** = navigation / work queue
- **Opportunity Workspace** = working area (opened from a selected deal)

## Primary nav

Dashboard → Contacts → **My Deals** → Loan Workspace → Tasks → Documents → Lenders → Accounting → Enterprise Intelligence → Horizon → Administration → Settings

## Architecture

- Vertical tabs (Loans live; MF / Insurance / etc. placeholders)
- Views: List (default), Kanban; Calendar / Analytics future
- Rows derived from LoanFile SSOT (`loadLoanFiles`) — no duplicate contact/deal store
- Double-click / card open → `buildJourneyHref(CREDIT_BENCH, { fileId, opportunityId })`

## Extending

Add a business vertical = new tab in `MY_DEALS_BUSINESS_TABS` + data adapter. No nav redesign.
